Mise.

LeRea v. Cochran, Director, Division of Corrections; Whiting v. Sacks, Warden; and Duke v. Ellis, Director, Texas Department of Corrections. Richard W. Ervin, Attorney General of Florida, and Reeves Bowen, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent in No. 581, Mise.

Motions for leave to file petitions for writs of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers submitted as petitions for writs of certiorari, cer-tiorari is denied.

Reported below: 115 So. 2d 545.
